author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Marvel are playing every card in the deck to drum up interest for Avengers Doomsday, but did it break the internet like they hoped, or was it just a desperate move for a company out of ideas? And as Snow White is on track to become the biggest box office bomb of the year, Rachel Zegler was publicly blasted by the son of the film's producer. Join me, MauLer, Disparu, Mr H Reviews and George The Giant Slayer at the Open Bar. 

Subscribe to Disparu: https://www.youtube.com/@disparutoo
Subscribe to Mr H: https://www.youtube.com/@MrHReviews
Subscribe to George: https://www.youtube.com/@GeorgeTheGiantSlayer
title: Open Bar #136 - Avengers Desperation, Zegler Blasted, Snow White Bombs
